                            </div>
                            <div class="imagediv fade"><img class="image" src="images/index_images/6.jpg" alt="">
                                <h2 class="imagetext">Explore the 'HELLO WORLD' !</h2>
                                <h1 class="imagetitle">Computer programming</h1>
                            </div>
                            <div class="imagediv fade"><img class="image" src="images/index_images/7.jpg" alt="">
                                <h2 class="imagetext">Explore every field of technology!</h2>
                                <h1 class="imagetitle">electrical electronics</h1>
                            </div>

                            <div class="imagediv fade"><img class="image" src="images/index_images/8.jpg" alt="">
                                <h2 class="imagetext">Explore every field of technology!</h2>
                                <h1 class="imagetitle">applied physics/ mathematics</h1>
                            </div>

                            <div class="dotdiv">
                                <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(1)"></span>
                                <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(2)"></span>
                                <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(3)"></span>
                                <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(4)"></span>
